import React from 'react'
import { NavLink, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Card, CardBody, CardLink, ListGroup, ListGroupItem, Nav } from 'reactstrap'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Nav className='navlink pt-5 pb-5 '>
      

      <ListGroup>
        <ListGroupItem>  <Link to='/' > Home </Link> </ListGroupItem>
        <ListGroupItem><Link to='/addreview' > Add Review </Link></ListGroupItem>
        <ListGroupItem><Link to='/viewreviews' > View Reviews </Link></ListGroupItem>
      </ListGroup>
      
     
      
      
       
      
      
    </Nav>
  )
}

export default Navbar
